location.fullValue: The Carriage House On Joy Street

description: Amazing oversized loft home open one bedroom....with ample closets...can easily become a 2 bedroom 2 bath, High ceilings, exposed bricks and beams.... one deeded parking space in the Courtyard can be purchased for $250,000. Well established condo building in Prime seaport location steps to all the city and the vibrant Seaport community has to offer....easy access to the T, Pike, Expressway, Amtrak , Logan and Fast Ferry to Provincetown all at your doorsteps... Trader Joe's  one block away, and Numerous dining and entertainment venues...Movies, Bowling , darts, pickle ball and so much more..Spacious open loft one bedroom with high ceilings, exposed bricks and beams. Washer/dryer, AC, amazing all new custom kitchen. with breakfast bar and barstools. Sunny eastern exposure. New Windows, and Heat pump system. . All new bathroom floor. Unit now has brand new vanity, and brand new hardwood floors. Live in this premiere loft building in the heart of the emerging seaport district.
